> alias deB64=3D"perl -MMIME::Base64 -e 'print decode_base64(shift @ARGV)=
'"

well ... i think perl is quite huge for this problem. I'll use openssl
as temporary hack.

alias B64enc=3D'openssl base64'
alias B64dec=3D'openssl base64 -d'

